    "body": "And FYI we do have the `.interpolate` method (which can call the spicy routines).\n\n``` python\nIn [34]: df.reindex((df.index + td / 2) | df.index).head()\nOut[34]:\n                          0   1   2\n2015-07-13 09:00:00.000   0  11   1\n2015-07-13 09:00:00.500 NaN NaN NaN\n2015-07-13 09:00:01.000   1  12   3\n2015-07-13 09:00:01.500 NaN NaN NaN\n2015-07-13 09:00:02.000   2  13   5\n\nIn [37]: df.reindex((df.index + td / 2) | df.index).interpolate().plot()\nOut[37]: <matplotlib.axes._subplots.AxesSubplot at 0x11d0df1d0>\n```\n\n![gh](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/1312546/8698172/0c52ab28-2ac1-11e5-901c-43994ea5ad6c.png)\n"
